---
title: Crispy-Skinned Chicken Thighs with Pear, Potato & Feta Salad
description: We love a good Chicken with Pear, Potato & Feta Salad and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crispy-skinned-chicken-thighs-0be28a3f-455dcd3d.jpg
